            <a name="usage"/>
            <subsection name="Usage">
                <ol type="1">
                    <li>Unzip
                        <tt>jlbc-1.0.0.zip</tt>
                        to the directory you wish to unzip it.
                    </li>
                    <li>To use jLBC add to your classpath the following jars:
                        <ol type="1">
                            <li>
                                <font style="font-weight: bold;color:red"><tt>jlbc_1.0.0-api.jar</tt></font>
                                and
                            </li>

                            <li>
                                <font style="font-weight: bold;color:red"><tt>jlbc_1.0.0-plaf.jar</tt></font>.
                            </li>
                        </ol>
                    </li>
                    <li>
                        If you want to use the implemented 
                        <a href="schemes/schemes.html">lattice-based cryptosystems</a>
                        include:
                        <ol>
                            <li>
                                <font style="font-weight: bold;color:green"><tt>jlbc_1.0.0-crypto.jar</tt></font>
                                and
                            </li>
                            <li>
                                <font style="font-weight: bold;color:green"><tt>bcprov-jdk16-140.jar</tt></font>.
                            </li>
                        </ol>
                    </li>
                </ol>
                <p>
                    All these libraries can be found in the jars folder.
                </p>
